							<!-- Lists -->
								<section>
									<!-- <h2>Lists</h2> -->
									<div class="row">
										<div>
											<h3>General Questions</h3>
											<ul class="alt">
												<li><strong>What is CozyCircles?</strong> 
													<p>
														CozyCircles is an online community designed to connect and support individuals with disabilities, their families, and caregivers. 
														It offers a warm and inclusive space for sharing experiences and fostering connections.
													</p>
												</li>
												<li><strong>Who can join CozyCircles?</strong>
													<p>
														CozyCircles is open to everyone, with a primary focus on individuals with disabilities, their families, and caregivers. 
														We welcome diversity and encourage anyone to join our community.
													</p>
												</li>
											</ul>
										</div>
										<div class="bd-top">
											<h3>Account Related</h3>
											<ul class="alt">
												<li><strong>How do i create an account on CozyCircles?</strong> 
													<p>
														To create an account, click on the <a href="accountcreation.html">"Create Account"</a> button, follow the registration process, and provide the required information.
													</p>
												</li>
												<li><strong>Can I link multiple account types to one profile?</strong>
													<p>
														At the moment, each user account is associated with a specific account type. 
														If you have different roles, consider creating separate accounts.
													</p>
												</li>
											</ul>
										</div>
										<div class="bd-top">
											<h3>Privacy and Security</h3>
											<ul class="alt">
												<li><strong>How is my privacy protected on CozyCircles?</strong> 
													<p>
														CozyCircles takes user privacy seriously. We have robust security measures in place to protect your data. Please refer to our <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> for detailed information.
													</p>
												</li>
												<li><strong>Is my information visible to everyone on the platform?</strong>
													<p>
														No, CozyCircles provides privacy controls allowing you to manage who can see your information. 
														You can customize your privacy settings in your account.
													</p>
												</li>
											</ul>
										</div>
										<div class="bd-top">
											<h3>Community Guidelines</h3>
											<ul class="alt">
												<li><strong>What are the community guidelines?</strong> 
													<p>
														Our community guidelines outline the expected behavior on CozyCircles. 
														We encourage all users to review and adhere to these guidelines to maintain a positive and supportive environment
													</p>
												</li>
											</ul>
										</div>
										<div class="bd-top">
											<h3>Troubleshooting</h3>
											<ul class="alt">
												<li><strong>I'm experiencing issues with my account. What should I do?</strong> 
													<p>
														If you encounter any problems, please reach out to our <a href="contact-us.html">Support Team</a> for assistance. 
														Provide detailed information about the issue for a prompt resolution.
													</p>
												</li>
											</ul>
										</div>
									</div>
								</section>
